        <updateDate>2008-06-10T21:49:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Saving Family Homes Act of 2008 - Grants eligible mortgagors subject to foreclosure proceedings the right to continue to occupy forclosed properties subject to the payment of fair market rent for a period of 20 years that begins upon the commencement of occupancy of such property. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
